devdoc.details: Smart contract for logging privacy decisions on-chain Stores hashed details to protect user privacy while maintaining transparency

getLog(uint256).details: Get a specific log by index

params.index: Index of the log to retrieve

returns._0: Log struct containing all privacy decision details

getUserLogs(address).details: Get all logs for a specific user

returns._0: Array of logs for the specified user
